<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<FlavorTextDefs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../Schema/FlavorText.xsd">

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_MAIN</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>什么肮脏的生物穿越了我的屏幕？</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>宇宙属于科拉斯，只属于科拉斯。我们将消灭任何敢在我们面前存在的生物。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>向你认为可以救你免于被Korath灭绝的任何东西跑去并哭泣。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我看到即使是帝国的废物也设法生存下来了。我猜如果你的情绪有所改善，我们可以尝试相处。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你与银河系的邪恶势力的交易将使所有人遭受厄运。如果有用，我们恳求你重新考虑你的历史进程。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>哦，不。我真的希望那些谣言是假的。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>那么，浪子部落回来了。你们是来再次向帝国屈膝了吗？作为我们的突击部队归来，宇宙将知道一个团结的帝国的恐怖。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_ARCEAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>德伦金人现在是在自相争斗吗？你对冲突的渴望真的无边无际吗？</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>无论你自称为何，我对德仁金毫无怜悯。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>不！这不可能。我以为帝国倒塌时，科拉斯氏族已被消灭。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>好的，联盟还活着。我会恨不得从未有机会报复。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>知道科拉斯氏族不会尊重德令帝国可能展示的任何仁慈。没有行动可以使你免于灭绝。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你们这种脆弱、微小的种族被允许生存的事实，证明了宇宙允许自己变得多么软弱。我们一定会纠正这一点。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>帝国失败了！你的锁链只会将你束缚在弱者身上。唯一的前进道路是毁灭！科拉斯氏族将继承德伦金的遗产。我们不需要你的弱点。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_YOR</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>别以为你们是金属制造的，我们就会饶了你们。灭绝对你们来说都是一样，我们会用你们破碎的身体来修复我们的武器和飞船。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你活下来了。这是帝国的又一次失败。科拉斯氏族不会犯同样的错误。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我们找到你了。你在宇宙的角落里躲藏了很久，但这次我们不会再失去你。科拉斯氏族终将扑灭你的幸存者团队。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_SEEING</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>这肯定是个笑话。你不可能活这么久。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_RESPONSE_PEACEFUL</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我希望我们的一些会面只是这么敌对。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>小心你的舌头，否则我会从你尖叫的头中拔出来。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你忘了科拉斯氏族不会施以仁慈。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>希望是弱者常犯的错误。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>哈！像帝国的那些弱小德伦金一样，根本不算是德伦金。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_ARCEAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>小心自己！科拉斯氏族不需要理由就能消灭弱者。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你不需要它。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>没有任何东西足够强大，能够消灭Korath Clan。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我们不需要保持这种敌意。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我希望如果有时间，你会重新考虑。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你会发现我们比看起来更有韧性。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>注意你的言辞！你不过是一个叛逆的军团。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_YOR</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>威胁已登记。我们预计结果会有变化。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>威胁再多也没用。我拒绝害怕你。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>抵抗军已做好应对你能做到的最坏情况的准备。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_SEEING</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我们不是笑话。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_RESPONSE_NEUTRAL</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我会等你发完脾气。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>尽情笑吧。科拉斯族会很快让你们灭绝。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我们在历史中的航程将是一次征服。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>投降，科拉斯会让你和你的恐惧安息。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你提供镣铐；我们将通过死亡，为你的耻辱提供解脱。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_ARCEAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>将此刻记住，你确保了自身的灭绝。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>不再受帝国规则的束缚，科拉斯终于可以把你从存在中抹去。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我还以为你们微不足道的抵抗已经被扫平了。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>尝试吧，我会很乐意提醒你我们对帝国做了什么。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_NAVIGATORS</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>那么，这个会议就此结束。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_MIMOT</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你以前被打败过；你还会再次失败。我不会担心的。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_DRENGIN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>对于疯狂的战争犬，只有一件事可做。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_YOR</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>对话==无用。终止通讯。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你并没有你想象的那么威胁。我要终止这次通信。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>抵抗力量熟悉你的策略。你对我们并无威胁。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_SEEING</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>我们累了。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TAUNT_PLAYER</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你的持续抵抗是徒劳的。科拉斯将确保你的灭绝。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>
	
	<FlavorTextDef>
        <InternalName>DECLARE_WAR_MAIN</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你的生活一定多么悲惨，不是我们中的一员。很快，你和你所有的同类都将结束。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_TERRAN</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你在德伦金的身边已经成为了一个刺。该是消灭你的时候了。十年之后，没有人会记得地球联盟。[BR][BR][COLOR=UIDefaultHighlight](我们正在战争中)[/COLOR]</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
				<ListenerFaction>FACTION_RESISTANCE</ListenerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你已足够长时间逃避你的命运了。科拉斯会踩灭你那些可怜的流浪者们。[BR][BR][COLOR=UIDefaultHighlight](我们正在战争中)[/COLOR]</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>GENERIC_GREETING</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>让这快点，外星渣滓。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>
		
	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TRADE_OFFER_REFUSE</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>在我把你拆散之前，重新考虑那个提议。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TRADE_OFFER_PERFORMED</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>不要认为这笔交易能保证你的安全。</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>TRADE_OFFER_WAITING</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>使这笔交易值得我花时间，否则我将强行夺取。</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>PLAYER_TRADE_COUNTER_OFFER_HEADER</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>好吗？</Text>
			<PreferenceWeight>50</PreferenceWeight>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>

	<FlavorTextDef>
		<InternalName>EXTRA_OPTIONS_MAIN_TEXT</InternalName>

		<FlavorTextOption>
			<Requirements>
				<SpeakerFaction>FACTION_KORATH</SpeakerFaction>
			</Requirements>
			<Text>你认为自己有资格与科拉斯交谈吗？</Text>
		</FlavorTextOption>

	</FlavorTextDef>
		
</FlavorTextDefs>
